<plot>Alex, a young father, has decided to put in second place his profession in order to take care of his two small children, something that will not be understood by his friends and work partners, neither by his own wife. Having children and bringing them up is not easy for anybody, but it is especially difficult for young urban couples where both parents have very demanding jobs. It is usually the mother who takes care of the children and has to give up work aspirations in order to be able to look after them, something that their husbands/couples are rarely aware of.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?135944</url></doc>
